sequenceDiagram
    actor Student
    participant LeaderboardUI as Leaderboard UI
    participant LeaderboardController as Leaderboard Controller
    participant Database

    Note over Student,LeaderboardUI: UC-06: View Leaderboard

    Student->>LeaderboardUI: Selects "Leaderboard" tab

    alt Offline Mode (PWA)
        LeaderboardUI->>LeaderboardUI: Load most recently cached data
        LeaderboardUI-->>Student: Display cached rankings with "Outdated" banner
    else Online
        LeaderboardUI->>LeaderboardController: getRankings(filter="All Time")
        LeaderboardController->>Database: queryRankings(filter)
        Database-->>LeaderboardController: return top_students (xp, streak, name)
        LeaderboardController->>LeaderboardController: calculateCurrentStudentRank()
        LeaderboardController->>Database: logEngagementEvent("leaderboard_viewed_at")
        LeaderboardController-->>LeaderboardUI: return leaderboard_data

        alt Fewer than 2 active students
            LeaderboardUI-->>Student: Display "Be the first to claim the
        else Data exists
            LeaderboardUI-->>Student: Display Top 10 + current student position & streak_count
        end
    end

    opt Filter Rankings
        Student->>LeaderboardUI: Selects time filter (e.g., "This Week")
        LeaderboardUI->>LeaderboardController: getRankings(filter="Weekly")
        LeaderboardController->>Database: queryRankings(time_window)
        Database-->>LeaderboardController: return filtered_students
        LeaderboardController-->>LeaderboardUI: refresh rankings view
        LeaderboardUI-->>Student: Update dashboard rankings
    end